{"parse":{"title":"Level 2 training","pageid":3000,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>Level 2 training is training given at an Accredited Training Organisation to the standards described in Model Course L2.0 for personnel having technical functions.\n</p><p><br />\n</p><p>Source: ENG7, Recommendation R0141\n</p>\n<div class=\"LanguageLinks\">\n<table width=\"100%\">\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\" style=\"background: #FFFFFF\">\n<td style=\"width: 25px; padding-left: 0em; border-right: 1px solid #aaaaaa;border-left: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-top: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-bottom: 1px solid #EEF3E2;\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:25px-Geographylogo.png\" class=\"mw-file-description\" title=\"Languages\"><img alt=\"Languages\" src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/8/82/25px-Geographylogo.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\" class=\"mw-file-element\" /></a></span></td>\n<td style=\"padding: 1px 1em 0; background: #EEF3E2;\">\n<p><b><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/Codes_on_Alerts_and_Indicators\" title=\"Codes on Alerts and Indicators\">English</a></b>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260617075239\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.029 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.036 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 58/1000000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 733/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 398/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/100\nExpensive parser function count: 4/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    9.466      1 Template:Languages\n100.00%    9.466      1 -total\n 63.05%    5.968      4 Template:Languages/Lang\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wiki_iala_dictionary_1_41:pcache:idhash:3000-0!canonical and timestamp